title: 7.Days.To.Die.Alpha.9.3.with.Integrated.AntiCheat.Working
description:
Hello again everyone!


This is a new and improved special package with integrated anticheat in order to circumvent cheating online.

For those who have this version and want to play online, you're welcome to join our server at:

198.50.158.241 port 25000

We also highly recommend using Teamspeak at the same IP in order to team up with other players.

Open 24/7, PVP Enabled with air drops and tons of zombies!


This version is different and won't allow others without the anticheat to join in to protect against cheating.

We have banned and will continue to ban all cheaters permanently from the server, luckily this version has helped protect against cheating very well.


Enjoy!
